data.title: McGillin's Olde Ale House
data.text:
Over the years, McGillin’s has attracted professional athletes, politicians, actors/actresses & rock stars.

You never know who you might meet at McGillin’s.

Here’s a list of some of the celebs spotted at McGillin’s:
